sequenceDiagram
    title Alert forensics feedback sequence
    participant RustProbe
    participant IngestGateway
    participant Kafka
    participant FlinkSession
    participant FlinkFeature
    participant DetectionJobs
    participant AlertGenerator
    participant DataStores
    participant GoAPI
    participant WebUI
    participant Analyst

    RustProbe->>IngestGateway: RegisterProbe and UploadFlows
    IngestGateway->>Kafka: Produce flow.events.v1
    Kafka->>FlinkSession: Consume FlowEvent
    FlinkSession->>Kafka: Produce session.events.v1
    Kafka->>FlinkFeature: Consume SessionEvent
    FlinkFeature->>Kafka: Produce feature.stat.v1
    Kafka->>DetectionJobs: Consume features and updates
    DetectionJobs->>Kafka: Produce detection event
    Kafka->>AlertGenerator: Consume detections
    AlertGenerator->>DataStores: Write alerts and evidence
    WebUI->>GoAPI: GET alerts and evidence
    GoAPI->>DataStores: Query alert context
    GoAPI-->>WebUI: Return alert detail
    Analyst->>WebUI: Mark TP FP and request PCAP
    WebUI->>GoAPI: POST feedback and PCAP job
    GoAPI->>Kafka: Produce alert.feedback.v1
    GoAPI->>DataStores: Write audit and task status
